description:
Kristofer Buckle, makeup artist to Queen of Christmas Mariah Carey—and so many other stars—dishes on the divas he works with and shares tips for reaching your full glam potential and adjusting your makeup as you age. We also talk about discontinued (and revamped) hair products, Racked.com's article on the swag editors receive, and milia, those tiny white bumps that can form around your eyes.

Become a member at https://plus.acast.com/s/fatmascara.
